sections.heading: Inquest; warrant of arrest; contents
sections.text: The warrant of the coroner shall recite substantially the verdict of the jury of inquest, and such warrant shall be a sufficient foundation for the proceedings of the justice instead of a complaint.SourceLaws 1879, ยง 108, p. 383;R.S.1913, ยง 5675;C.S.1922, ยง 5005;
